🛠 Troubleshooting
500 error on import
JSON not closed properly
Trailing comma
Missing microseconds
Wrong null type
Missing required field
Extra field not in schema
ID references a non‑existent VM/hardware
Hardware won’t import
You used UI fields the backend doesn’t store
You omitted backend‑only fields
You used empty strings instead of null
Timestamp format wrong
Apps won’t import
vm_id doesn’t exist
hardware_id is not null
external_hostname is not null
IDs don’t start at 1
---
🧭 Recommendations
Always export first to see the real schema
Never trust the UI fields
Build imports category‑by‑category
Validate JSON with a linter
Keep IDs small and sequential
Use null instead of empty strings
Include microseconds in timestamps
